                  "fill": "#848484",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "When dragging hits a minimum boundary, the handle stops moving and the cursor remains col-resize. The panel being resized will not go below its minimum. react-resizable-panels enforces these constraints via the minSize/maxSize props (percentage-based).",
